Ruby/GLib2
==========
Ruby/GLib2 is a Ruby binding of GLib-2.x.

Requirements
------------

  Ruby >= 1.9.x: http://www.ruby-lang.org/
  pkg-config.rb: http://github.com/rcairo/pkg-config
  GLib >= 2.x: http://www.gtk.org/

Install (RubyGems)
------------------

  % sudo gem install glib2

Windows:

  > gem install glib2 --platform x86-mingw32

Install (traditional)
---------------------

Install ruby-1.9.x or later, pkg-config.rb and GLib-2.x.

  % ruby extconf.rb
  % make
  % sudo make install

